snippet.title: Sumsub
snippet.description:
We live in a time when the internet is assuming a massive role in our lives. And it’s not just because we can order new shoes from the bathroom or stream seven seasons of The Office in a row. Today, the internet poses very real dangers for our privacy, personal security, and even our identities. We’re here to help you stay safe. Ready to venture into the online jungle with us?


Every week we upload a new video, offering unique insights from the security experts at Sumsub--an international company that builds tools to fight money laundering, terrorist financing, and online fraud.
